Company Name: Whole Body At Whole Foods Mkt
Company Description: Whole Body At Whole Foods Market Is A Department That Features A Selection Of Natural Cosmetic And Body Care Products. Founded IN 1980 As A Small Store IN Austin, Texas, Whole Foods Market Has Become One Of The Leading Retailers Of Natural And Organic Foods With More Than 150 Stores IN The United States. It Operates Various Subsidiaries, Including Pigeon Cove, Select Fish And Allegro Coffee Company. Whole Body Retails Cosmetics That Contain Vitamins And Antioxidants. It Also Retails Body Care Products, Wellness Supplements, Nutritional Products, Moisturizers, Eyeliners, Face Packs And Conditioners. IN Addition, Whole Foods Market Offers Diets, Snacks, Appetizers, Salads, Desserts, Muffins, Seafood And Pasta, As Well As Soups And Juices. It Also Provides Soy Foods, And Low-Sodium And Gluten-Free Products. The Company Offers Various Recipes, Kitchen Tips, Promotions And IN-Store Discounts. It Operates Multiple Stores IN New York.
